Items.mt: One hundred years ago, before the three schools were separated, they all originated from the same Zangmo school. The most powerful technique in this school is called Zangmo Sword Technique. The most powerful technique in this school is called the Zangmo Sword Technique. Shan Mo Wu did not pass on his technique to his three true disciples.
